4. Detailed study of shell ï¬nite element discretizations As discussed above, the shell ï¬nite elements based on the basic shell mathematical model are equivalent to the continuum mechanics based shell ï¬nite elements. We next use the shell ï¬nite elements based on the basic shell mathematical model to perform a detailed study of the strain components in ï¬nite element discretizations as obtained using either discretization approach as the shell thickness decreases.

